quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  33,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  33,1,ae paighambar khuda se drtay rehna aur kafiroon aur mnafqon ka kaha nah maanna. be shak khuda jan-nay wala aur hikmat wala hai
  33,2,aur jo ( kitaab ) tum ko tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se wahi ki jati hai usi ki pairwi kiye jana. be shak khuda tumahray sab amlon se khabardaar hai
  33,3,aur khuda par bharosa rakhna. aur khuda hi karsaaz kaafi hai
  33,4,khuda ne kisi aadmi ke pehlu mein do dil nahi banaye. aur nah tumhari aurton ko jin ko tum maa keh baithtay ho tumhari maa banaya aur nah tumahray le پالکوں ko tumahray betay banaya. yeh sab tumahray munh ki baatein hain. aur khuda to sachhi baat farmata hai aur wohi seedha rasta dekhata hai
  33,5,momino! le palikoo ko unn ke ( asli ) bapon ke naam se puraka karo. ke khuda ke nazdeek yahi baat durust hai. agar tum ko unn ke bapon ke naam maloom nah hon to deen mein woh tumahray bhai aur dost hain aur jo baat tum se ghalti se hogayi ho is mein tum par kuch gunah nahi. lekin jo qasad dili se karo ( is par muwakhza hai ) aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  33,6,paighambar mominoun par unn ki jaanun se bhi ziyada haq rakhtay hain aur paighambar ki biwiyan unn ki maaen hain. aur rishta daar aapas mein kitaab allah ke roo se musalmanoon aur mhajron se aik dosray ( ke trke ) ke ziyada haqdaar hain. magar yeh ke tum apne doston se ahsaan karna chaho. ( to aur baat hai ). yeh hukum kitaab yani ( quran ) mein likh diya gaya hai
  33,7,aur jab hum ne payghambaroon se ehad liya aur tum se Nooh se aur ibrahim se aur moose se aur maryam ke betay eesa se. aur ehad bhi unn se pakka liya
  33,8,taakay sach kehnay walon se unn ki sachaai ke baray mein daryaft kere aur is ne kafiroon ke liye dukh dainay wala azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  33,9,momino khuda ki uss meharbani ko yaad karo jo ( uss ne ) tum par ( uss waqt ki ) jab faujein tum par ( hamla karne ko ) ayen. to hum ne unn par howa bhaije aur aisay lashkar ( nazil kiye ) jin ko tum dekh nahi satke they. aur jo kaam tum karte ho khuda unn ko dekh raha hai
  33,10,jab woh tumahray ooper aur neechay ki taraf se tum par charh aeye aur jab ankhen phir gayeen aur dil ( maaray dehshat ke ) gulon taq poanch gay aur tum khuda ki nisbat terhan terhan ke gumaan karne lagey
  33,11,wahan momin aazamaa_e gay aur sakht tor par hlaye gay
  33,12,aur jab munhafiq aur woh log jin ke dilon mein bemari hai kehnay lagey ke khuda aur is ke rasool ne hum se mehez dhokay ka wadakiya tha
  33,13,aur jab unn mein se aik jamaat kehti thi ke ae ahal madinah ( yahan ) tumahray theharnay ka maqam nahi to lout chalo. aur aik giroh un mein se paighambar se ijazat mangnay aur kehnay laga ke hamaray ghar khulay parre hain halaank woh khulay nahi they. woh to sirf bhagna chahtay they
  33,14,aur agar ( faujein ) atraaf madinah se un par aa daakhil hon phir unn se khanah jungi ke liye kaha jaye to ( foran ) karne lagen aur is ke liye bohat hi kam tawaquf karen
  33,15,halaank pehlay khuda se iqraar kar chuke they ke peeth nahi phrin ge. aur khuda se ( jo ) iqraar (kiya jata hai uss ki ) zaroor prssh hogi
  33,16,keh do ke agar tum marnay ya maaray se bhagtay ho to bhagna tum ko faida nahi day ga aur is waqt tum bohat hi kam faida uthao ge
  33,17,keh do ke agar khuda tumahray sath buraiee ka iradah kere to kon tum ko is se bacha sakta hai ya agar tum par meharbani karni chahay to ( kon is ko hata sakta hai ) aur yeh log khuda ke siwa kisi ko nah apna dost payen ge aur nah madadgaar
  33,18,khuda tum mein se un logon ko bhi jaanta hai jo ( logon ko ) mana karte hain aur apne bhaiyon se kehte hain ke hamaray paas chalay aao. aur larai mein nahi atay magar kam
  33,19,( yeh is liye ke ) tumahray baray mein bukhal karte hain. phir jab dar ( ka waqt ) aeye to tum un ko dekho ke tumhari taraf dekh rahay hain ( aur ) unn ki ankhen ( isi terhan ) phir rahi hain jaisay kisi ko mout se ghashi aa rahi ho. phir jab khauf jata rahay to taiz zabanon ke sath tumahray baray mein zabaan Darazi karen aur maal mein bukhal karen. yeh log ( haqeeqat mein ) imaan laaye hi nah they to khuda ne un ke aamaal barbaad kar diye. aur yeh khuda ko aasaan tha
  33,20,( khauf ke sabab ) khayaal karte hain ke faujein nahi gayeen. aur agar lashkar ajayeen to tamanna karen ke ( kash ) ganwaroon mein ja rahen ( aur ) tumhari khabar poocha karen. aur agar tumahray darmain hon to larai nah karen magar kam
  33,21,tum ko paighambar khuda ki pairwi ( karni ) behtar hai ( yani ) is shakhs ko jisay khuda ( se milnay ) aur roz qayamat ( ke anay ) ki umeed ho aur woh khuda ka zikar kasrat se karta ho
  33,22,aur jab mominoun ne ( kafiroon ke ) lashkar ko dekha to kehnay lagey yeh wohi hai jis ka khuda aur is ke paighambar ne hum se wadakiya tha aur khuda aur is ke paighambar ne sach kaha tha. aur is se un ka imaan aur itaat aur ziyada hogayi
  33,23,mominoun mein kitney hi aisay shakhs hain ke jo iqraar onhon ne khuda sekiya tha is ko sach kar dekhaya. to un mein baaz aisay hain jo apni Nazar se farigh hogaye aur baaz aisay hain ke intzaar kar rahay hain aur onhon ne ( apne qoul ko ) zara bhi nahi badla
  33,24,taakay khuda schon ko unn ki sachaai ka badla day aur mnafqon ko chahay to azaab day aur ( chahay ) to unn par meharbani kere. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  33,25,aur jo kafir they unn ko khuda ne phair diya woh apne ghusse mein ( bharay hue they ) kuch bhalai haasil nah kar sakay. aur khuda mominoun ko larai ke baray mein kaafi howa. aur khuda taaqatwar ( aur ) zabardast hai
  33,26,aur ahal kitaab mein se jinhon ne unn ki madad ki thi unn ko unn ke qlaon se utaar diya aur unn ke dilon mein dehshat daal di. to ktnon ko tum qatal kar dete they aur ktnon ko qaid kar lete they
  33,27,aur unn ki zameen aur un ke gharon aur un ke maal ka aur is zameen ka jis mein tum ne paon bhi nahi rakha tha tum ko waris bana diya. aur khuda har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
  33,28,ae paighambar apni biwion se keh do ke agar tum duniya ki zindagi aur is ki zeenat vaaraysh ki khawastgah ho to aao mein tumhe kuch maal dun aur achi terhan se rukhsat kardoon
  33,29,aur agar tum khuda aur is ke paighambar aur aqibat ke ghar ( yani bahisht ) ki tallab-gaar ho to tum mein jo نneko karikarne wali hain unn ke liye khuda ne ajar azeem tayyar kar rakha hai
  33,30,ae paighambar ki byoyo tum mein se jo koi Sarih na shaista ( alfaaz keh kar rasool allah ko aeza dainay ki ) harkat kere gi. is ko dunne saza di jaye gi. aur yeh ( baat ) khuda ko aasaan hai
  33,31,aur jo tum mein se khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmanbardar rahay gi aur amal naik kere gi. is ko hum dona sawab den ge aur is ke liye hum ne izzat ki rozi tayyar kar rakhi hai
  33,32,ae paighambar ki byoyo tum aur aurton ki terhan nahi ho. agar tum parhaizgaar rehna chahti ho to kisi ( ajnabi shakhs se ) naram naram baatein nahkiya karo taakay woh shakhs jis ke dil mein kisi terhan ka marz hai koi umeed ( nah ) peda kere. aur un dastoor ke mutabiq baatkiya karo
  33,33,aur apne gharon mein thahri raho aur jis terhan ( pehlay ) jahliat ( ke dinon ) mein izhaar Tajammal karti theen is terhan zeenat nah dikhao. aur namaz padti raho aur zakaat deti raho aur khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmabardari karti raho. ae ( paighambar ke ) ahal beeet khuda chahta hai ke tum se napaaki ( ka mil kuchail ) daur kardey aur tumhe bilkul pak saaf kardey
  33,34,aur tumahray gharon mein jo khuda ki ayatain parhi jati hain aur hikmat ( ki baatein sunai jati hain ) un ko yaad rakho. be shak khuda bareek been aur bakhabar hai
  33,35,( jo log khuda ke agay sir itaat khham karne walay hain yani ) musalman mard aur musalman aurtain aur momin mard aur momin aurtain aur farmaa bardaar mard aur farmaa bardaar aurtain aur raast baz mard aur raast baz aurtain aur sabr karne walay mard aur sabr karne wali aurtain aur farotni karne walay mard aur farotni karne wali aurtain aur khairaat karne walay mard aur aur khairaat karne wali aurtain aur rozay rakhnay walay mard aur rozay rakhnay wali aurtain aur apni sharamgahon ki hifazat karne walay mard aur hifazat karne wali aurtain aur khuda ko kasrat se yaad karne walay mard aur kasrat se yaad karne wali aurtain. kuch shak nahi ke un ke liye khuda ne bakhshish aur ajar azeem tayyar kar rakha hai
  33,36,aur kisi momin mard aur momin aurat ko haq nahi hai ke jab khuda aur is ka rasool koi amar muqarrar kar dein to woh is kaam mein apna bhi kuch ikhtiyar samjhain. aur jo koi khuda aur is ke rasool ki nafarmani kere woh Sarih gumraah hogaya
  33,37,aur jab tum is shakhs se jis par khuda ne ahsaankiya aur tum ne bhi ahsaankiya ( yeh ) kehte they ke apni biwi ko apne paas rehne day aur khuda se dar aur tum apne dil mein woh baat posheeda karte they jis ko khuda zahir karne wala tha aur tum logon se drtay they. halaank khuda hi is ka ziyada mustahiq hai ke is se daro. phir jab Zaid ne is se ( koi ) haajat ( mutaliq ) nah rakhi ( yani is ko Talaq day di ) to hum ne tum se is ka nikah kardiya taakay mominoun ke liye un ke munh bolay biton ki biwion ( ke sath nikah karne ke baray ) mein jab woh un se apni haajat ( mutaliq ) nah rakhen ( yani Talaq day den ) kuch tangi nah rahay. aur khuda ka hukum waqay ho kar rehne wala tha
  33,38,paighambar par is kaam mein kuch tangi nahi jo khuda ne un ke liye muqarrar kardiya. aur jo log pehlay guzar chuke hain un mein bhi khuda ka yahi dastoor raha hai. aur khuda ka hukum ٹھیر chuka hai
  33,39,aur jo khuda ke pegham ( jon ke ton ) pohanchate aur is se drtay hain aur khuda ke siwa kisi se nahi drtay they. aur khuda hi hisaab karne ko kaafi hai
  33,40,Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam tumahray mardon mein se kisi ke waalid nahi hain balkay khuda ke paighambar aur nabiyo ( ki nabuwat ) ki mohar ( yani is ko khatam kardainay walay ) hain aur khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  33,41,ae ahal imaan khuda ka bohat zikarkiya karo
  33,42,aur subah aur shaam is ki paki bayan karte raho
  33,43,wohi to hai jo tum par rehmat bhejta hai aur is ke farishtay bhi. taakay tum ko andheron se nikaal kar roshni ki taraf le jaye. aur khuda mominoun par meharban hai
  33,44,jis roz woh is se milein ge un ka tohfa ( khuda ki taraf se ) salam hoga aur is ne un ke liye bara sawab tayyar kar rakha hai
  33,45,ae paighambar hum ne tum ko gawahi dainay wala aur khushkhabri sunanay aur darane wala bana kar bheja hai
  33,46,aur khuda ki taraf bulanay wala aur chairag roshan
  33,47,aur mominoun ko khushkhabri suna do ke un ke liye khuda ki taraf se bara fazl hoga
  33,48,aur kafiroon aur mnafqon ka kaha nah maanna aur nah un ke takleef dainay par nazar karna aur khuda par bharosa rakhna. aur khuda hi karsaaz kaafi hai
  33,49,momino! jab tum momin aurton se nikah karkay un ko haath laganay ( yani un ke paas jaane ) se pehlay Talaq day do to tum ko kuch ikhtiyar nahi ke un se adt poori karao. un ko kuch faida ( yani kharch ) day kar achi terhan se rukhsat kardo
  33,50,ae paighambar hum ne tumahray liye tumhari biwiyan jin ko tum ne un ke mohar day diye hain halal kar di hain aur tumhari londiyan jo khuda ne tum ko ( kufar se bator maal ghanemat ) dilwai hain aur tumahray chacha ki betiyan aur tumhari phupiyon ki betiyan aur tumahray mamoon ki betiyan aur tumhari khalaon ki betiyan jo tumahray sath watan chore kar aayi hain ( sab halal hain ) aur koi momin aurat agar apne tain paighambar ko bakhash day ( yani mohar lainay ke baghair nikah mein aana chahay ) bashart e kay paighambar bhi un se nikah karna chahain ( woh bhi halal hai lekin ) yeh ijazat ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) khaas tum hi ko hai sab musalmanoon ko nahi. hum ne un ki biwion aur londion ke baray mein jo ( mohar wajib alada ) muqarrar kardiya hai hum ko maloom hai ( yeh ) is liye (kiya gaya hai ) ke tum par kisi terhan ki tangi nah rahay. aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  33,51,( aur tum ko yeh bhi ikhtiyar hai ke ) jis biwi ko chaho alehda rakho aur jisay chaho apne paas rakho. aur jis ko tum ne alehda kardiya ho agar is ko phir apne paas talab karlo to tum par kuch gunah nahi. yeh ( ijazat ) is liye hai ke un ki ankhen thandhi rahen aur woh ghumnaak nah hon aur jo kuch tum un ko do. usay le kar sab khush rahen. aur jo kuch tumahray dilon mein hai khuda usay jaanta hai. aur khuda jan-nay wala aur Burdbar hai
  33,52,( ae paighambar ) un ke siwa aur aurtain tum ko jaaiz nahi aur nah yeh ke un biwion ko chore kar aur biwiyan karo khuwa un ka husn tum ko ( kaisa hi ) acha lagey magar woh jo tumahray haath ka maal hai ( yani londion ke baray mein tum ko ikhtiyar hai ) aur khuda har cheez par nigah rakhta hai
  33,53,momino paighambar ke gharon mein nah jaya karo magar is soorat mein ke tum ko khanay ke liye ijazat di jaye aur is ke paknay ka intzaar bhi nah karna parre. lekin jab tumhari dawat ki jaye to jao aur jab khana کھاچکو to chal do aur baton mein jee laga kar nah baith raho. yeh baat paighambar ko aeza deti hai. aur woh tum se sharam karte hain ( aur kehte nahi hain ) lekin khuda sachhi baat ke kehnay se sharam nahi karta. aur jab payghambaroon ki biwion se koi samaan mango to parday ke bahar mango. yeh tumahray aur un ke dono ke dilon ke liye bohat pakizgee ki baat hai. aur tum ko yeh Shayaan nahi ke paighambar khuda ko takleef do aur nah yeh ke un ki biwion se kabhi un ke baad nikah karo. be shak yeh khuda ke nazdeek bara ( gunah ka kaam ) hai
  33,54,agar tum kisi cheez ko zahir karo ya is ko makhfi rakho to ( yaad rakho ke ) khuda har cheez se bakhabar hai
  33,55,aurton par apne bapon se ( parda nah karne mein ) kuch gunah nahi aur nah apne biton se aur nah apne bhaiyon se aur nah apne bhtijon se aur nah apne bhanjon se nah apni ( qisam ki ) aurton se aur nah londion se. aur ( ae aurtoo ) khuda se darti raho. be shak khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  33,56,khuda aur is ke farishtay paighambar par duroood bhaijtay hain. momino tum bhi un par Duroood aur salam bheja karo
  33,57,jo log khuda aur is ke paighambar ko ranj pohanchate hain un par khuda duniya aur akhirat mein laanat karta hai aur un ke liye is ne zaleel karne wala azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  33,58,aur jo log momin mardon aur momin aurton ko aisay kaam ( ki tohmat se ) jo unhon ne nahkiya ho aeza den to unhon ne bohtan aur Sarih gunah ka boojh apne sir par rakha
  33,59,ae paighambar apni biwion aur baityon aur musalmanoon ki aurton se keh do ke ( bahar nikla karen to ) apne ( monhon ) par chadar latka ( kar ghonghat nikaal ) liya karen. yeh amar un ke liye mojab shanakht ( o imtiaz ) hoga to koi un ko aeza nah day ga. aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  33,60,agar munhafiq aur woh log jin ke dilon mein marz hai aur jo madeeney ( ke shehar mein ) buri buri khabrain udaya karte hain ( apne kirdaar ) se baz nah ayen ge to hum tum ko un ke peechay laga den ge phir wahan tumahray paros mein nah reh saken ge magar thoray din
  33,61,( woh bhi ) phatkaray hue. jahan paye gay pakdae gay aur jaan se maar daaley gay
  33,62,jo log pehlay guzar chuke hain un ke baray mein bhi khuda ki yahi aadat rahi hai. aur tum khuda ki aadat mein tagayur o tabdeel nah pao ge
  33,63,log tum se qayamat ki nisbat daryaft karte hain ( ke kab aeye gi ) keh do ke is ka ilm khuda hi ko hai. aur tumhekiya maloom hai shayad qayamat qareeb hi aagai ho
  33,64,be shak khuda ne kafiroon par laanat ki hai aur un ke liye ( jahannum ki ) aag tayyar kar rakhi hai
  33,65,is meinabdul aabaad rahen ge. nah kisi ko dost payen ge aur nah madadgaar
  33,66,jis din un ke munh aag mein ultaye jayen ge kahin ae kash hum khuda ki farmabardari karte aur rasool ( khuda ) ka hukum mantay
  33,67,aur kahin ge ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum ne apne sardaro aur barray logon ka kaha maana to unhon ne hum ko raste se gumraah kardiya
  33,68,ae hamaray perwar-digaar un ko dugna azaab day aur un par barri laanat kar
  33,69,momino tum un logon jaisay nah hona jinhon ne moose ( ko aib laga kar ) ranj pohanchaya to khuda ne un ko be aib saabitkiya. aur woh khuda ke nazdeek aabaroo walay they
  33,70,momino khuda se dara karo aur baat seedhi kaha karo
  33,71,woh tumahray aamaal durust kardey ga aur tumahray gunah bakhash day ga. aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmabardari kere ga to be shak barri morad paye ga
  33,72,hum ne ( baar ) amanat ko asmano aur zameen par paishkiya to unhon ne is ke uthany se inkaarkiya aur is se dar gay. aur ensaan ne is ko utha liya. be shak woh zalim aur jaahil tha
  33,73,taakay khuda munhafiq mardon aur munhafiq aurton aur mushriq mardon aur mushriq aurton ko azaab day aur khuda momin mardon aur momin aurton par meharbani kere. aur khuda to bakhsnay wala meharban hai
